"title": "5817: conspiracies",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5817: conspiracies",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Malicious plots or plans to harm or to kill, which may be directed against other people, or even against God. Conspiracies are sometimes motivated by political aspirations, but may be simply an outlet for wrongdoing.</p>\n<h2>Conspiracies to sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:3\">MIC 7:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:2\">PSA 52:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:6\">PSA 64:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:27\">PRO 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:30\">PRO 16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:9-Jer11:10\">JER 11:9–11:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:25\">EZK 22:25</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies to murder</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:23\">JER 18:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:17-Gen37:23\">GEN 37:17–37:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:17\">2SA 11:2–11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:20-2Chr24:21\">2CH 24:20–24:21</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies to commit genocide</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:24-Esth9:25\">EST 9:24–9:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1-2Sam21:6\">2SA 21:1–21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:5-Esth3:9\">EST 3:5–3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies to hinder the work of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:7-Neh4:8\">NEH 4:7–4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:11\">NEH 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:15\">NEH 4:15</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies against kings</h2>\n<h3>Conspiracies to overthrow the king</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:10\">2KI 15:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:25-1Kgs15:28\">1KI 15:25–15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:8-1Kgs16:10\">1KI 16:8–16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:15-1Kgs16:18\">1KI 16:15–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:14-2Kgs9:24\">2KI 9:14–9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:9-2Kgs10:11\">2KI 10:9–10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:19-2Kgs12:21\">2KI 12:19–12:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:25-2Chr24:26\">2CH 24:25–24:26</a> <em>the assassination of Joash</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:17-2Kgs14:19\">2KI 14:17–14:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:27\">2CH 25:27</a> <em>the assassination of Amaziah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:15\">2KI 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:23-2Kgs15:25\">2KI 15:23–15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:30\">2KI 15:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:23-2Kgs21:24\">2KI 21:23–21:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:24-2Chr33:25\">2CH 33:24–33:25</a> <em>the assassination of Amon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:21-Esth2:22\">EST 2:21–2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:2\">EST 6:2</a></p>\n<h3>Conspiracies against King David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:10-2Sam15:12\">2SA 15:10–15:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:7-1Sam23:13\">1SA 23:7–23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:15\">1SA 23:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:19-1Sam23:23\">1SA 23:19–23:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:31\">2SA 15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:5-1Kgs1:10\">1KI 1:5–1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:28\">1KI 2:28</a></p>\n<h3>False accusations of conspiracy against kings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:10-Amos7:11\">AMO 7:10–7:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:6-1Sam22:8\">1SA 22:6–22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:13-1Sam22:16\">1SA 22:13–22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:5-Neh6:9\">NEH 6:5–6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:9\">DAN 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies against cities and nations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:2\">JER 48:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:5-Isa7:6\">ISA 7:5–7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:30-Jer49:33\">JER 49:30–49:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:2-Ezek11:3\">EZK 11:2–11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:24-Dan11:25\">DAN 11:24–11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:10\">HAB 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies against God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1-Ps2:3\">PSA 2:1–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:11\">PSA 21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps83:5-Ps83:8\">PSA 83:5–83:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:11-Hos7:16\">HOS 7:11–7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:9-Nah1:11\">NAM 1:9–1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies against God's servants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:20-2Chr24:21\">2CH 24:20–24:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:13\">PSA 31:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:4\">PSA 35:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:4\">PSA 36:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:12\">PSA 37:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:12\">PSA 38:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:2\">PSA 52:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:5\">PSA 56:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:3\">PSA 59:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:2\">PSA 64:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:10\">PSA 71:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps83:3\">PSA 83:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:24-Ps105:25\">PSA 105:24–105:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:18-Jer11:19\">JER 11:18–11:19</a> <em>a plot against Jeremiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:23\">JER 18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:60-Lam3:61\">LAM 3:60–3:61</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies against Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:14\">MAT 12:14</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:6\">MRK 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:11\">LUK 6:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:3-Matt26:4\">MAT 26:3–26:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:1\">MRK 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:1-Luke22:2\">LUK 22:1–22:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:53\">JHN 11:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:27\">ACT 4:27</a></p>\n<h2>Conspiracies against Paul</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:12-Acts23:16\">ACT 23:12–23:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:20-Acts9:25\">ACT 9:20–9:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:1-Acts14:7\">ACT 14:1–14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:12\">ACT 18:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:3\">ACT 20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:19\">ACT 20:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:30\">ACT 23:30</a></p>\n<h2>Conspirators condemned</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:15-Isa33:16\">ISA 33:15–33:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:1-2Sam12:12\">2SA 12:1–12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:29\">PRO 3:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:12-Prov6:15\">PRO 6:12–6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:20\">PRO 12:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:22\">PRO 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:1-Prov24:2\">PRO 24:1–24:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:8\">PRO 24:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:12\">ISA 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1\">MIC 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16-Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:16–8:17</a></p>",
